> Wow. Had a really interesting morning...
>
> Wife came up to me asking when the bus was going to be sold. I
> explained there was only one person from this list who had expressed
> an interest, and that I hadn't really made any efforts to advertise
> it. I didn't even have a ForSale sign up.
>
> She actually BEGGED me to keep it!
>
> I was stunned, and told her so. She said she really liked it and it
> was worth losing me a day a week working on it. Well, how could I say
> no to that? So we're keeping it. :-)
>
> I want to thank all of the listees who helped remind me why I bought
> the bus in the first place, and talked me into waiting a bit before
> selling. I guess it took a week for my wife to get up the nerve to
> intrude on "my" domain (cars). I've saved all your wonderful emails
> and am printing them out and putting them in a folder to keep in the
> bus as a reminder of what being a bus owner is all about.
>
>

